data.description:
Rare 5 Bedroom 3 bath with bonus loft ! Prime westside location with great schools and access to shopping and all services. The white picket fence gives great curb appeal and the inside also delivers. Formal Living and dining room lead to the open family room/Cooks kitchen. The granite kitchen comes with Stove wall ovens dishwasher and microwave. 1BR 1BA downstairs with tile/laminate floors. Upstairs is the primary bedroom, 2 large and 1 huge bedrooms as well as a small loft/nook/office area. The 3 car garage offers workshop/mancave possibilities and the rear turf yard is low maintenance and an entertainers delight. Solar panels help with the monthly bills too!
$4200 Tenant pays all services - Water Trash and Gardening.1 year lease. Strong financials. First and Security. No Pets. No Prior evictions.
